GSD.product_version: versions from v3.10 to before v6.0.17
GSD.description:
SUNRPC: Don't leak netobj memory when gss_read_proxy_verf() fails

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.17 by commit 67eb848161c2799f2007968ea3bc87adb15c9567, it was introduced in version v3.10 by commit 030d794bf49855f5e2a9e8dfbfad34211d1eb08b. For more details please see the references link.
